Bot-Babelfish
=============

DESCRIPTION

    This distribution includes a module that provides Babelfish 
    translation services through an IRC bot. A program eg/babelbot 
    is included as example.


INSTALLATION

    To install this module, run the following commands:

        perl Makefile.PL
        make
        make test
        make install

    Alternatively, to install with Module::Build, you can use the 
    following commands:

        perl Build.PL
        ./Build
        ./Build test
        ./Build install


